    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Morphological characteristics to differentiate the genera of Lestidae: (A) Archilestes, (B) Lestes.Abbreviations: a (proximal side of the triangle), b (posterior side of the triangle), H (pterothorax total high), W (pterothorax total width)." ;
